column4:
こんなもの、
どうするつもりなんだよ。
column5: What exactly are you planning to do with these things?
column11: What exactly are you planning to do with these things?

column5: Use them to decorate my eighth villa.
column11: Use them to decorate my eighth villa.

column4:
庭に置く彫刻を探している時に、
遺跡の噂を聞いてね。
column5: I heard a rumor about these ruins when I was looking for some sculptures to put in the garden.
column11: Whilst I was looking for some sculptures to put in the garden, I heard a rumour about these ruins.

column4: うん。なかなかいいものね。
あなたたちも、ご苦労様。
column5: Thank you for your hard work.
column11: Thank you for your hard work.
